    <abstract>
      <para>This volume represents a compilation of topics concerning Firebird's SQL language
      written by members of the Russian-speaking community of Firebird developers and users.
      In 2014, it culminated in a language reference manual, in Russian. At the instigation
      of Alexey Kovyazin, a campaign was launched amongst Firebird users world-wide
      to raise funds to pay for a professional translation into English, from which translations
      into other languages would proceed under the auspices of the Firebird Documentation
      Project.</para>
    </abstract>

